UI Preset: Heritage Atlas
Purpose

Create an optional UI preset called Heritage Atlas that transforms Flowscape into an application that feels like a beautifully crafted historical engineering atlas rather than modern engineering software.

The goal is not fantasy or medieval styling. Instead, imagine if transportation engineers, architects, and surveyors from the late 1800s or early 1900s had access to modern simulation software while retaining the artistic craftsmanship of printed atlases, architectural plans, and illuminated technical books.

This preset should affect only the visual presentation. All functionality, workflows, shortcuts, and interactions remain identical.

Core Design Principles

The interface should communicate:

Precision
Craftsmanship
Elegance
Timelessness
Engineering professionalism

Rather than flat modern UI, every element should appear intentionally designed and carefully composed, with an emphasis on balance, symmetry, and refined detail.

The application should feel like a collector's edition engineering reference book.

