Interface Philosophy

The UI should not resemble software designed in Figma or another modern design tool.

Instead, it should resemble an authentic page from an antique botanical manuscript that has somehow become interactive.

The player should feel as though they are opening an enchanted illustrated field guide rather than using a conventional application.

